      • type

        public final String type()
        Type of the lens mapping. Supported values are gnomonical, stereographic, equidistant, equisolid_angle, orthographic, custom. For gnomonical (perspective) projection, it is recommended to specify a horizontal_fov of less than or equal to 90°

      • type

        public final Lens.Builder type(String value)
        Type of the lens mapping. Supported values are gnomonical, stereographic, equidistant, equisolid_angle, orthographic, custom. For gnomonical (perspective) projection, it is recommended to specify a horizontal_fov of less than or equal to 90°

      • intrinsics

        public final Intrinsics intrinsics()
        Camera intrinsic parameters for setting a custom perspective projection matrix (cannot be used with WideAngleCamera since this class uses image stitching from 6 different cameras for achieving a wide field of view). The focal lengths can be computed using focal_length_in_pixels = (image_width_in_pixels * 0.5) / tan(field_of_view_in_degrees * 0.5 * PI/180)

      • intrinsics

        public final Lens.Builder intrinsics(Intrinsics value)
        Camera intrinsic parameters for setting a custom perspective projection matrix (cannot be used with WideAngleCamera since this class uses image stitching from 6 different cameras for achieving a wide field of view). The focal lengths can be computed using focal_length_in_pixels = (image_width_in_pixels * 0.5) / tan(field_of_view_in_degrees * 0.5 * PI/180)
